
REQUIREMENTS
============

1. Development
--------------
JDK 1.6.0 U20
Groovy 1.7.x
Griffon 0.3.1
	Plugins:
	glazedlists 0.3
	jide-builder 0.3
	spring 0.2
	swingx-builder 0.1
	swingxtras-builder 0.2
	tray-builder 0.3

2. Runtime
----------
JDK 1.6.0 U20


ARCHITECTURE
============

1. MVC
------
Model: a bindable Map in ProjektModel.groovy
View: render data, use controller for actions
Controller: reads data from view, update model, publish events
Events: perform calculations using a service, update model
Services: contain business logic


HINTS
=====
Groovy + Debugging: http://groovy.codehaus.org/Debugging+with+JSwat
